race.description: Bhp Nickel West 2025 Leinster Cup Hcp (Bm64+)
race.comment: BOAB BOY (1) finished second two runs back at Kalgoorlie then improved scoring by 10 lengths bet deep into the red over 1600m at Leonora. The leader keeps the handy 3kg claim and can go on with the job. DANCING JACK (3) placed second in that race, coming off two Stakes races at Kalgoorlie. Good enough at best and may be worth another chance on the surface. GOT LUCKY (2) was unwanted in betting last time but scored by 0.8L over 1800m at Mt Magnet. Sound record at this distance and with a low barrier and 2kg claim can make the finish. MONEY FOR OLD ROPE (6) also found the top selection much too good at Leonora but has pieces of form that would see him competitive.
